Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was left at the altar in front
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of the entire town. My
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,fiance vanished. The guests
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,behind my back, and the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,debt fell on me like a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence. Within days, I lost my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,job,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,my home, and what little dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had left. That
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was when Ludovico Caracolo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared. The most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,feared man in Providence offered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,me away out. He'd pay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,everything. Clear my name, and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.55,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I agreed to be his wife on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,paper, I thought I was entering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a cold contract. But soon I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,discovered my fiance hadn't just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,run away, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico knew far more than he
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,let on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lena. A special shout
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,out to those of you watching
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Book
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One for free here on the My
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stories platform, completely ad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-free and uninterrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 1. The bell told for the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,last
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the bouquet trembled in my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't decide whether
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the weight of the roses,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,or the weight of the waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence church
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of melted wax and old
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,lilies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that two sweet perfume that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,clung to the throat. The priest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,had already checked the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time, he smiled at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you tried to calm a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,child. The second. He turned his
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to avoid my eyes. The third, he
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't even bother pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. All of Providence was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,seated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,behind me. I felt the murmur
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,rise up the back of my white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,dress like a cold current, a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,whisper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that swelled with every passing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,minute. The women in the fifth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,row had stopped disguising their
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,whispering. One of them laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,low, held back, and I heard it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I heard everything in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Russell of fans, the shuffle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of feet, the tick-tock of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,old clock at the back of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nave, a delmo had set the time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for 11 o'clock. It was ten to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,noon. Narina was right behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first row, squeezing the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,back of my hand as if she could
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,hold me in place by the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers. She didn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. Narina had a comment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything, a joke even at a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,funeral,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and her silence right then was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the most terrifying thing that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,happened to me that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I closed my eyes, took a deep
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,breath, counted to ten. I opened
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,my eyes, and the church door was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,empty. I, Landa, Narina murmured
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,close to my ear. Sweetheart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,don't talk. My voice came out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,steady, low, but steady. If you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,talk, I'll fall apart. She
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,squeezed my hand again, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,bell began.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One toll, noon, two tolls. The
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,priest came down from the altar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and walked over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Three tolls. The women in the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,fifth row were no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing. Four tolls. Five, six,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,eleven, twelve. The bell told
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for the last time, and the echo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hung in the church's vaulted
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like something dirty, ugly to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,look at. No one moved, no one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,coughed. All of Providence held
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,its
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,breath at the same time, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,felt in my shoulders the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,moment the town understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,collectively, that I had been
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,abandoned. The priest stopped in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,front of me, hands folded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was pity in his eyes, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,pity is the one thing a bride
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't know where to put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My child? No. I clutched the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,bouquet to my chest. You don't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have to say anything. I turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,back on him. Basing the altar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,was easier than facing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence, but the church had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,only one way out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and that way passed by every
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar face. Every stare from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,those who had come to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what they were now seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Narena stood up with me. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,coming with you. She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,one step at a time. I started
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,walking. One step, then another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The dress dragged behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And every inch of that fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,weighed like a remnant of what I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,had imagined that morning would
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I had imagined laughter. I had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,imagined a shy kiss at the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,altar. I had imagined a delmo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,squeezing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,my elbow with that nervous way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of his whispering, I'm here, I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,here. A delmo hadn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed the third row. Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Marchetti, my neighbor for ten
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,years, lowered her head. I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,passed the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,fifth row, and no one was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing anymore. I passed the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,distant cousin a delmo had
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,invited at the last
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,minute, and he avoided my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with a haste that almost broke
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Narena held my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look ahead, just ahead. We
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the door. The sunlight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,outside hit my eyes, and for a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,moment I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. And in that white blaze
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of light, I almost believed I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was going to wake up from the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,whole
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,morning that it had all been a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,bad last minute dream. It
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't. I went down the stone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,staircase slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because going down fast was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,admitting that I wanted to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had decided without
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that Providence would not see me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,run. The stones were worn in the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,middle, the iron railing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,darkened by age. Each step
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,caused the same effort as a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,breath. A yellow taxi stopped at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,at the corner of the square. I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't called it. Narena had. I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,got in. She got in after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Federal Hill, she told the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,driver. End of atwells near
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Salve's bakery. The driver
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in the rear view mirror. Saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,white dress. Saw my face and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask anything. He started
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the car in silence. I rested my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,forehead against the glass. The
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,city rushed past outside. The
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,statue
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in the square. Old Salve's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,bakery. The corner where Adelmo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,had kissed me for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,years ago. On that corner, he
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,had told me he would love me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,until the day the world forgot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,how to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The world had turned just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that morning. I got home before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my feet. Narena opened
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the door to my apartment. Went
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in first. Started turning on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lights. I stood in the middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,dress. Still holding the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,bouquet. And looked around like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,someone visiting a stranger's
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was still in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The cup I had washed before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving. The book left open on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the arm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sofa. The empty vase
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for the wedding flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat on the floor. I just sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The dress billowed around me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cloud. And I didn't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because crying was asking too
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of the body at that hour. I just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,sat there with the bouquet in my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,lap and stared at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Narena sat down next to me on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor. Without taking off
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,her shoes, without smoothing her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She rested her head on my
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder and stayed. He'll show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,up. I said, something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,An accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Something. Narena didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Narena. No. What do you mean no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to show up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ielanda. She lifted her head and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,looked me in the eye. If it had
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,been an accident, someone would
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,have
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,called. If something had
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,happened, his family would be at
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the church. No one was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one. I stayed quiet. She was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,right. That morning, none of the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,reachy's had shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not his mother. Not his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No one. I had seen it. And I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunday passed without my
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,remembering it. Monday morning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the phone rang. The principle of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,school where I'd been teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,literature for four years called
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,me by my full surname with a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,strange
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,formality. And I already knew
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before she finished the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence. Ielanda, it's not a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,good time to keep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher involved in scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Scandal? I leaned against the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen wall. I was jilted Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Peretti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't caught stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence on the other end. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the mothers are talking. You
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher needs an intact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,reputation. Reputation. I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,repeated. The reputation of a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,woman who was humiliated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in public is the reputation she
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,lost. Ielanda, please. Please. I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,said, yes. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I hung up. I stood in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen. My hands still on the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,phone. And felt nothing. No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,anger. No shock. No tears. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a very
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,polite emptiness. Like the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,emptiness of a room after the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,guests have gone. Tuesday
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,morning the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,collectors began. The first one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,showed up at eight in a dress
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt and carrying a black
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And said my name over the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,intercom with a casualness that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,froze my blood. He came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sat in my living room like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd been there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the briefcase and handed me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You signed here. His finger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped beneath my signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to Adele Moes. Wedding paid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,for with borrowed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,money. $12 ,000. Do in 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sign any loan. He
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,turned the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,paper toward me. It was my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,writing. It was my signature. It
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was right there. Beneath a line
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of text I didn't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now that I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,closely, the signature had been
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,collected in the pile. Along
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,one, Moe asked me to sign just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,some boring forms. Love from the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,venue. I had signed without
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The man waited for me to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,understand. When I did, he
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the briefcase. You have
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd rather pay an
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,installments, there's interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd rather negotiate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there are partners. Take your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,pick. He stood up. We're
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,watching. He left. I didn't move
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for a stretch of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,time. I can't measure. Then I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,went to the window and saw his
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,car parked across the street. I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,kept
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,watching. He didn't look up. He
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't need to. He had already
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me enough. That
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:08:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the second man showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday morning the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday morning, the eviction
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,taped to the apartment door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina arrived that night with a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,grocery bag and the serious face
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,she
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,almost never wore. She set the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,bag on the table. Pulled out a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,bottle of wine. Pulled out a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,butter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,knife. I brought wine and a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,butter knife. She said, pick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,first. I laughed before I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,realized I was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,laughing. It was an ugly laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,short, lasting a second, but it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was a laugh. And Narina
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized it the way you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize a friend's voice after
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,years. Butter knife. I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,handle wine tonight. She set the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,wine aside. Set down. Took off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,her shoes. Do you have anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Do you have money? No. Do
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a plan? Narina. If I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,had a plan, I wouldn't be
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,holding a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,dinner knife. She squeezed my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,arm. Stayed like that for a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,while. You're staying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you need. My couch is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ugly, but it's mine. I nodded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. I didn't know if I was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,thanking her or refusing. Both
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,things at once, maybe. She
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed late. Cooked pasta with
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was in the pantry. Made me eat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,three forkfuls. Took the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,dress off the hanger where
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it had hung since Saturday and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,carried it away without asking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Tomorrow I'll burn it. She
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,said
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the door or donated to charity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide later. I decided
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,later. E. Wednesday morning and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope arrived. It was on the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,floor by the door when I went
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,down to get the newspaper out of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because I wanted to read the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,news, but because going down the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs was the only gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the day that still felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,mine. The envelope was of thick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,paper, the color of old cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,no stamp, no postmark. Just my
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,name written in the center. In
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,firm, tall handwriting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly slanted to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eolanda, Marcecano. No one wrote
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,my full name like that. Not even
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,my father wrote my full name
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,like that when he was still
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,alive. I went up the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday the kitchen table,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the envelope carefully as
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if something might escape from
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only a card. Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Veccia Roma. Tomorrow. 5pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I have a solution for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,L.C. I stared at the three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,letters. L.C. Two initials an
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,period at the end. Like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,economizes even with letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence had three ways of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,pronouncing those initials. And
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,meant the same person. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Caracolo. The man the whole town
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,bowed its head to. The man my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,father had forbidden me to look
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at when I was a child. And saw a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,procession of black cars passing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,down at Wells Avenue. Don't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,look, Eolanda. He had said, that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,car in the middle is the car we
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,tend doesn't exist. I was little
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I looked anyway. I saw no
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,one. The glass was too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that same man had written my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,name with his own hand. He knew
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my address. He knew of my shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew of my debt. He probably
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,knew more things about me than
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,my ex-fiancey new. I set the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:11:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,card
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,down on the table. I ran my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,finger slowly over the L. The
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ink still smelled almost almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it was my imagination. Picturing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that fresh ink as a way of him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,being closer. I closed my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of the eviction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed tape to the door. I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of the man with a black
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,briefcase
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,watching my building from across
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the street. I thought of Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Pairetti calling me miss with
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,disgust. I thought of Narina on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,her ugly couch. And how much she
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,deserved to sleep in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a ruined friend breathing in her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,living room. I opened my eyes. I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't go to the cafe because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to. I went because I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,had nowhere left to run. Chapter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,two, the offer from the man the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,town fears. Cafe Vichia Roma sat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,on a corner of the old
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood where time had
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,decided
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,at some point to stop passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark wooden doors smoked glass
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,windows. A discreet bell that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,rang when I pushed the door
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,open. And the noise inside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,dropped. It didn't drop because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stairs at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,shifted. In a small synchronized
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,movement toward the table at the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,back. And the table at the back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,had a man sitting at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico Caracciolo was dressed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,dark from shoulders to shoes. A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,suit cut with precision. A white
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt open at the top button,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,no tie. A cup of coffee resting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in his right hand. His wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,exposed. An old watch with a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,worn strap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised his eyes when the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,rang. And saw me before I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,decided what to do with my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark hair combed back. Two days
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,worth of stubble. His eyes were
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the worst. Eyes that already
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,knew
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,me before I arrived. As if he
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,had memorized my face before I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,even reached the door. I walked
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't stand. He didn't pull
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,out the chair. He just watched
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,me come. And the whole cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,watched
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,me come with him. I sat. Miss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcicano. His voice was low.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper than I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Words spaced out. Like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,choosing them one at a time and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,giving up on the ones he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,missed her caracciolo. I set my
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,purse on my lap. You know all of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence is looking at this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,table. All of Providence looks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at any table I sit at. He
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,brought the cup to his lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Took a small sip. It's not about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you. What a relief. The corner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of his mouth twitched slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a smile. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sketch of a thought he decided
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not to finish. A waiter appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,hand behind his back. Bent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to be respectful. What
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,will you have, Mam? Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No sugar today. The waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,nodded and disappeared. Lutavico
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,watched me order. He didn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You called for me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,straightened my shoulders. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,here. If you have something to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like preamble. I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,have time for preamble. He set
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the cup down slowly on the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,saucer. The clink of porcelain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was the only sound at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for a moment. You owe $12,000
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Costanza Brothers. He
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,said. Neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,loan-sharking. You lost your job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on Monday. You lost your
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment on Wednesday. You have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a friend who offered you her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,couch. You have no living
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,relatives and providence. And
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the fiancé? Enough. I cut in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made your point. He
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilted his head a fraction of a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeter in a gesture that was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,almost a thank you for my
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,frankness. I was going to say he
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,continued that the fiancé is a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,matter you still don't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But today isn't the day for that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation. And what day is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that conversation? A day that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,next five minutes. The waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,returned with my coffee. I took
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a sip too quickly and burned my
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,tongue on purpose to have a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,physical reason to pay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,attention. And say it. I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lutavico rested
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,his elbow on the table. The old
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,watch gleamed in the low light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I erase every cent of your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I buy the Costanza's papers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,tonight. I give you back the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment if you want or arrange
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,another
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,one. I handle the school
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,problem. Mrs. Peretti will get a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,phone call and remember that she
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,likes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you. You're describing a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,miracle. I'm describing a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,transaction. His eyes didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,waver. In exchange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for a single thing. I took
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,another sip. I didn't let my
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,hand tremble. What thing? You
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On paper. The cafe kept making
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee around me. The steam wand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,cut through the air. Someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed at a distant table. And
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat there listening to the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,most feared man in Providence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,offer me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a contract marriage with the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,same calm you'd order the check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a marriage proposal? I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,said
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly or a purchase order. He
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,almost smiled. Again, he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,smile. It's a proposal. You can
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get up from this table
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,right now. And the only thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do is pay for your coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow the Costanza brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,still exist. And the eviction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,notice is still taped to the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I held the cup more firmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage on paper. I repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean exactly? A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,civil contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,City Hall. No religious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony. He began counting the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,rules on his fingers. Without
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lifting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand from the table. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,moving them one by one. You live
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in my house. You have your own
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another. Both doors stay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,closed. Go on. In public, you're
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife. You go to events with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You smile when it's time to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,smile. You don't need to pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,more than that. In private?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't touch you. I won't go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,into your room. I won't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,about your life. And you won't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ask about mine. No questions. No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,questions. I set the cup on the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,saucer. I thought that no
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,questions had the smell of a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,locked door. And locked doors
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,were exactly the ones I always
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long? One year. After
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that, you can ask for the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,separation without any contest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd rather stay longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's negotiable. Why me? It was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the first question of mine that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,took
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a second longer to answer. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a second. Because you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice dropped half a tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And because I need a wife for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,reasons that don't fit into this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation, I held his gaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He held mine. Neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,blinked for a stretch of time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that would have been awkward at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,any other
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,table. I'll think about it. I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,said, you haven't till tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. Me. He took from the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,inner pocket of his jacket, a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,cream-colored card with tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,firm handwriting. The address of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you show up, it's yes. If you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,don't, it's no. I took the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fingers didn't touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but they passed so close that I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,felt the warmth of his hand for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second before I pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,mine back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always negotiate like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this? I asked, two sentences in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a card? No. He leaned back in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,his
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,chair. But with you, I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,want to make things up. I stood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,up from the table. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,thank him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for the coffee. He didn't expect
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,me to. I walked to the door with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,my back straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing all of Providence would
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,be recounting this scene for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks. When I touched the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard behind me, low, almost
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thought aloud. Two sugar cubes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a drop of milk. I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked over my shoulder. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico didn't look at me. He
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,was stirring his own coffee with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,small spoon. That's how you take
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it. When you're not testing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood there a second longer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,than I should have. Then I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the door and left. Err. I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,slept badly. I woke before the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I shoured. Put on the least
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,wrinkled blue dress in my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,closet. Gathered my documents
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,into a small
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,bag and went down the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,without saying goodbye to a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,single thing. I left a short
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,note
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for Narina on the kitchen table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that explains nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and promises everything. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the scolding later. City
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hall was three blocks from the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,harbor. I arrived 15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he was already there. Leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,against the corridor wall, hands
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in his jacket pockets,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at his own shoe like
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd been waiting long
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to have memorized the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Beside him, an older man, broad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldered, with the look of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd come back from
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wars
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,no one had named. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,raised his head when he saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't smile. He made no
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He just waited for me to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. I said, good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. He made a discreet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the man beside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion del Rose. He works with
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,me. He'll be nearby whenever you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion tilted his head half a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,degree. No hello, no pleasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,no smile, just the half degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I answered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway. Because my grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,would have smacked me if I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The clerk called us. We went
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,into a small room with a long
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,table. Papers already prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico pushed them toward me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,before the clerk could open his
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth. Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly. If there's any claws you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,don't accept, we redo it. I read
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,every line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly the way he'd said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the cafe. Separate rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,appearances in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions. One year. Right of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,unilateral exit on her part. I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the last page and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,slid my finger down to the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,signature line. I saw nothing I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't supposed to see. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I said. I signed. He
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,signed after me. The clerk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,stamped it. There was no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss. No photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No rice thrown on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us left City Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in silence. The car was waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Black, glossy, glass too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind my father used to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,me not to look at when I was a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion opened the rear door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico got in from the other
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,side and sat next to me without
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The car took the road toward the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,upper suburb. Providence shrank
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in the window. The red rooftop
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,falling away behind us and green
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,took over. He didn't speak the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,entire way. Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The mansion gate appeared after
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,20 minutes. Dark iron, tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with a discreet crest in the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,center.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A lion's head with the crown
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,split in two. I didn't ask what
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it meant. It was part of the no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate opened. The car went up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a lane of low trees. I saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,house before I knew it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Three stories of pale stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,tall windows, a double staircase
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,at the entrance. A small woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,my grandmother's age, appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,at the door above. Her pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,into a low bun, white apron,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,dry hands, Donachyata, Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,said, this is Yolanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachyata looked me over from
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,head to toe,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,not with judgment, with concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of look only a kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,woman knows how to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome. She said, you must be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,tired. I'm fine. She didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,believe me, but she
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,not did and didn't insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico took me upstairs. The
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,upper corridor was long, with
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,identical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,doors on both sides. He stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,at the third door on the right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and opened it. This is your
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too big for one person. A
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,canopy double bed, a desk at the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,window, a built-in closet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,along an entire wall. Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in shades of cream and gray, a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,tasteful cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My room is at the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. He said, behind me, on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the left side,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to go past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood? If you need
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,anything, Donachyata is always
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, he paused a second. If
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you need me, Donachyata knows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,where I am. I turned to look at
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was standing in the doorway,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,one hand on the handle, looking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,at some point between my
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder and the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,window. But the first time since
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the cafe, he seemed unsure of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,where to put his gaze. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I wasn't quite sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He tilted his head a fraction of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a millimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the door. I heard his
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps go down the corridor,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and silence. I sat on the edge
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran my hand over the duvet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fabric was soft in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that made my eyes sting without
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't cry. Not that first
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.74,0:23:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon. That night,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachyata came up with a tray,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hot soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,fresh bread, a glass of red
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.99,0:23:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,wine. I didn't ask her to swap
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it for water. I drank the wine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,last drop. I laid down without
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,changing my clothes and stared
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,at the ceiling of the canopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Near midnight, I heard footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the corridor, slow, measured
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps. They came from the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,end of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:23:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor. They reached my
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,door. They stopped. They stood
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there for a stretch of time. I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.32,0:24:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Five seconds. Ten. More than
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,ten. He didn't knock. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,call out. He made no sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.32,0:24:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the footsteps went back. I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.05,0:24:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,heard them move away slowly. The
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,same rhythm in the direction
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they had
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,from. The door at the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor opened. Closed. I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,stared at the canopy in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,position
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and understood, lying in that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,bed too big for one person, that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the man the town feared had come
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.76,0:24:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to my door on the first night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.93,0:24:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to come in, not to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Only to stop outside, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.20,0:24:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I closed my eyes. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep. Chapter three. House
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,rules, the man's gestures.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Karachiolo mansion woke before I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.06,0:24:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,did. I discovered this on the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.60,0:24:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,first morning. When I came down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.24,0:24:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the marble stairs still in my
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,robe, fastened up to my neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.98,0:24:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and found the house already
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.62,0:24:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara, tidying the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.87,0:24:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,sideboard in the hall. The smell
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:24:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of fresh bread coming from the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:24:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.14,0:25:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A staff member I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.21,0:25:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize cleaning the vestibule
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.71,0:25:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,stained glass with silent
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.87,0:25:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.88,0:25:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No one looked at me as if I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.16,0:25:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't belong there. No one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.45,0:25:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me as if I belonged
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.83,0:25:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,either.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.16,0:25:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worse than hostility. It
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.28,0:25:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,was professional neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.20,0:25:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, ma'am. Donachiyara
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.40,0:25:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.14,0:25:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing me standing in the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.45,0:25:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen archway. Coffee here or
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.07,0:25:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the garden room. It took me a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.75,0:25:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,second
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand that ma'am was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is fine. I answered. If
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.13,0:25:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not in the way, she laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.30,0:25:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.36,0:25:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of laugh only Italian
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.62,0:25:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,women of a certain age know how
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.93,0:25:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to give without taking their
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.11,0:25:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hands
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.32,0:25:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,off their apron. You. In the way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.39,0:25:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in my kitchen. That's a good
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.20,0:25:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,one. I sat on the wooden bench
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.15,0:25:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,against
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.74,0:25:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara set a cup in front
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.26,0:25:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of me without asking how I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.58,0:25:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted it. Two sugar cubes had
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.10,0:25:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,been
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.30,0:25:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,dissolved in it. A drop of milk
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.10,0:25:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,had been added on top. The
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.61,0:25:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee was exactly the color I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.47,0:25:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,been
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.70,0:25:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,drinking since I was 15. I held
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.64,0:25:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the cup with both hands. Did you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.65,0:25:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,tell Mr. Ludovico?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.48,0:25:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara kept stirring a pot
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.02,0:25:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,on the stove without turning
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.41,0:25:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,around. No one needed to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,anything
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,my dear. Mr. Ludovico left it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.27,0:26:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,noted. He asked that it be this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.27,0:26:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,way every day. She paused
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.88,0:26:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Always. I drank the coffee too
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.50,0:26:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. That was how the first
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,week went. I'd discover a house
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.78,0:26:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,rule by accident. And Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.56,0:26:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,had already altered the rule in
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,silence so I'd fit inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.32,0:26:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On Monday, I mentioned aloud to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.95,0:26:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Donachiyara that I missed the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.48,0:26:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,bookside left in my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.72,0:26:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,On Tuesday, three of my
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.02,0:26:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,favorites were on the little
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.60,0:26:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,table in my room with new
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.01,0:26:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,bookmarks
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.52,0:26:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,between the pages. On Wednesday,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.41,0:26:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Bastion I hated the black
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.31,0:26:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,car because it reminded me of a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.14,0:26:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,general. I only said it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.46,0:26:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sarcastically because he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.95,0:26:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared in a dark suit in the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.68,0:26:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor and I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.48,0:26:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to provoke him. On
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.85,0:26:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday, Bastion appeared at
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.44,0:26:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the winter garden door with his
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.14,0:26:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,hands folded
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.80,0:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of his body, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.46,0:26:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,stone face that was already his
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.18,0:26:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,trademark. He asked me to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.79,0:26:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,whether
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.18,0:26:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd prefer the gray car or the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.04,0:26:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,black one to go out today. I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.68,0:26:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,looked up from my book. Do I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.31,0:26:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,have
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.54,0:26:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,something scheduled today? You
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.77,0:26:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,will, if you want to. He blinked
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.15,0:27:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,once. Bastion, I said, trying
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.31,0:27:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,not to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.76,0:27:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,where you always like this or
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.62,0:27:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,where you trained. Both, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.60,0:27:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And he went back down the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.20,0:27:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor with a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.16,0:27:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,step identical to the one he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.67,0:27:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived with. I kept staring at
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.23,0:27:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the door for half a minute with
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.80,0:27:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the book
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.20,0:27:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten in my lap. And
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.41,0:27:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,admitted to myself that this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.83,0:27:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,house was starting to become an
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.40,0:27:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,intimate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,joke I hadn't asked to be part
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.76,0:27:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of. The problem was, the joke
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.65,0:27:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,had an owner. And the owner of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.60,0:27:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.80,0:27:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,joke didn't smile. Ludovico and
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.06,0:27:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I crossed paths with icy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.81,0:27:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,formality. In the corridor, he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.15,0:27:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,nod,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.44,0:27:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,half a degree, enough not to be
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.64,0:27:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,rude. At dinner, we sat at the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,two ends of the long table
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.62,0:27:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,like two chess pieces pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the board was too big for any
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.99,0:27:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,attack. He'd ask if I'd needed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.64,0:27:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.72,0:27:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd answer no. He'd ask if Dona
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.72,0:27:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiara had been kind. I'd answer
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that she was an angel. He'd
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.54,0:27:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,fold his napkin and stand up. No
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.52,0:27:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,questions. That was the rule. He
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.50,0:27:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kept the rule better than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.00,0:27:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday evening, Narina showed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.43,0:27:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,up at the gate with a leather
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:27:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,bag that looked like it weighed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.12,0:28:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,more than she did. Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.70,0:28:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,opened the gate for her without
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.58,0:28:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,arguing. Dona Chiara hugged her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.46,0:28:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,like a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.82,0:28:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,relative. Narina walked through
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.48,0:28:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the hall with wide eyes and a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.04,0:28:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,comment on the tip of her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.38,0:28:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.16,0:28:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This place looks like a museum
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.78,0:28:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with tasteful ghosts. I pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.39,0:28:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,her into the kitchen before
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.85,0:28:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.28,0:28:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,could appear. Sweetie, she
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.09,0:28:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,whispered, taking a Tupperware
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.18,0:28:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,container out of her bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.36,0:28:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my grandmother's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.91,0:28:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,lasagna, not that Dona Chiara
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.64,0:28:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,needs help, but my grandma liked
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.54,0:28:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.78,0:28:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't going to let that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.73,0:28:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,slide. Your social hazard. I
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.55,0:28:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,know. Where does he sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.92,0:28:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina. Just so I know the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.39,0:28:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,distance between the two rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.08,0:28:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,missing. It's field research.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.28,0:28:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We sat on the kitchen bench,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.01,0:28:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,split the lasagna into two
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.61,0:28:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,bowls, and ate in secret like
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.40,0:28:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.58,0:28:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,teenagers who'd snuck out of the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.18,0:28:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,cafeteria. It was the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.79,0:28:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd laughed since the church
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.19,0:28:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.74,0:28:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed for real. My face half
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.77,0:28:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered, almost choking on a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.55,0:28:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,piece of cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.36,0:28:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dona Chiara passed by the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.36,0:28:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,pretended not to see, and kept
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.29,0:28:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,going toward the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.46,0:29:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico passed by the door five
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.63,0:29:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes later. He also pretended
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.81,0:29:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,not to see, but I saw him. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.78,0:29:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,had his shirts leave rolled up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.50,0:29:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to the elbow, his hair a little
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.28,0:29:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,out of place. The kind of detail
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.12,0:29:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.18,0:29:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't have registered. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.79,0:29:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped in the archway for half
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.51,0:29:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a second. Exactly long enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.28,0:29:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,identify me laughing, and kept
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.02,0:29:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,going down the corridor without
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.81,0:29:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,saying anything. Narina gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.60,0:29:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.66,0:29:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,sweet kick on the foot under the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.76,0:29:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,bench. Sweetie, she whispered,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.72,0:29:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mouthful, that man just looked
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.69,0:29:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.08,0:29:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you look at an open
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.50,0:29:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,window in the middle of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.13,0:29:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, it's a professional
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.61,0:29:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.04,0:29:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your music teacher Narina. Music
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.97,0:29:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is observation, my girl. What do
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.91,0:29:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you think we listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.54,0:29:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I nudged her with my elbow. She
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.27,0:29:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed. Dona Chiara came back
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.94,0:29:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,with a picture of water as if
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.55,0:29:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.94,0:29:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,had happened. I took a long sip
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.95,0:29:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and said nothing more. That
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.69,0:29:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,night, when Narina left, the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.50,0:29:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.28,0:29:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,too silent. I passed the library
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.51,0:29:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,door and saw the light on under
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:29:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the crack. I didn't go in. I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:29:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,went to my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.00,0:30:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the door, and took a long
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.87,0:30:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,time to fall asleep. The kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.73,0:30:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,was too big for crying at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.92,0:30:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered this three days
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.57,0:30:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,later, on Monday, when I came
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.28,0:30:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,down barefoot at three in the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.99,0:30:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.00,0:30:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'd woken with my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.69,0:30:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in my throat, and a dream of an
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.38,0:30:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,empty church stuck to my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.02,0:30:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned on only the light above
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.94,0:30:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the stove. I sat on the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.62,0:30:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,floor with my back against the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.42,0:30:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.38,0:30:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The crying came without sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.02,0:30:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I'd learned to cry when
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.72,0:30:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived with my grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.88,0:30:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and she didn't like to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.43,0:30:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,sadness after ten at night. I
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.09,0:30:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,heard the footsteps before I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.93,0:30:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,his
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.10,0:30:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,shadow in the archway. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.77,0:30:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,turn on the main light. He stood
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.45,0:30:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,there for two seconds in the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.91,0:30:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,door
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.12,0:30:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,way. In a white shirt open at
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.96,0:30:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the collar. His hair sang he
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.73,0:30:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't slept either. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.64,0:30:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.46,0:30:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I lifted my chin before he could
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.12,0:30:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,think of touching me. I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.62,0:30:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,need an audience to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. He stopped in a very
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.19,0:30:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,specific way, without retreating
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.09,0:30:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or advancing. He just stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.32,0:30:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, without saying a word, he
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.06,0:30:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the kitchen, opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.80,0:31:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cabinet beside my shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.90,0:31:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and took out a glass. He filled
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.46,0:31:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the glass with water at the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.81,0:31:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sink. He set the glass on the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.27,0:31:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,floor near my knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.68,0:31:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He sat on the floor across from
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.42,0:31:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,me. His back against the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.77,0:31:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite cabinet. His legs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.23,0:31:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,stretched out
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.96,0:31:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way that made his feet
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.82,0:31:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,almost touch mine. And he
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.54,0:31:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed. He didn't talk. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.32,0:31:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.58,0:31:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't offer a shoulder. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.53,0:31:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there. On the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.16,0:31:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen floor, with his rumpled
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.17,0:31:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.50,0:31:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and his gaze on some point
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.06,0:31:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,between my knee and the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.44,0:31:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,baseboard, breathing slowly. I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.24,0:31:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,cried for two more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.34,0:31:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I drank half the glass. I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.37,0:31:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a little more. I drank the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.86,0:31:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When I stood up, he stood up
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.61,0:31:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,too, without touching me. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.35,0:31:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,collected the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.60,0:31:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Carried it to the sink. Washed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.46,0:31:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it with the same calm he did
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.19,0:31:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.56,0:31:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Ayolanda. I went
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.10,0:31:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,back to my room and took a long
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.81,0:31:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,time to fall asleep again,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.68,0:31:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but for another reason. The
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.23,0:31:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,first public dinner came on
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.77,0:31:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.98,0:31:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Il Juita Sole. A restaurant that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.78,0:31:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,served all of Providence without
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.59,0:32:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,serving anyone properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.54,0:32:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with a crystal chandelier and a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.42,0:32:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,mehta, who lowered his head half
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.36,0:32:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a degree when Ludovico entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.24,0:32:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd told me at breakfast with a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.19,0:32:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,short sentence. In the way I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.89,0:32:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,already recognized as his way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of asking without asking. Il
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.59,0:32:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Juita Sole, nine at night. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.73,0:32:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,important that we appear
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.38,0:32:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.54,0:32:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dress? Whatever you think is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.30,0:32:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,good. I chose the dark blue one,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.32,0:32:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the one with thin straps that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.14,0:32:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,fell to mid-caf. I put on the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.47,0:32:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,only pair of earrings I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.61,0:32:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,brought from the old department.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.54,0:32:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I came down the stairs with my
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.20,0:32:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hair pinned at the nape and saw
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.91,0:32:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico waiting below
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.12,0:32:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in a black suit that looked like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.74,0:32:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it had been cut on his body, and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.37,0:32:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,an expression he managed to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.74,0:32:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,keep closed for three seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.01,0:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,before looking away. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said. At the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.47,0:32:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.20,0:32:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No one stared. We sat at a table
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.03,0:32:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,near the back. The mait report
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.74,0:32:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the wine with slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.00,0:32:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,trembling hands. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.41,0:32:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ordered for me without
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.66,0:32:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,consulting me. A dish I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.47,0:32:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,have ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.72,0:32:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was exactly the way I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.37,0:33:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,liked it. I raised an eyebrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.03,0:33:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Donachiyara have a notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.79,0:33:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.90,0:33:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my records? I asked. She has a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.82,0:33:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,memory. Her memory is about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.81,0:33:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about everyone who sits at her
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.74,0:33:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,table.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.64,0:33:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a sip. Ludovico, he
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.14,0:33:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,looked up. Does this still feel
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.93,0:33:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,more like a contract than a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.48,0:33:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.48,0:33:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He held the glass by the stem,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.13,0:33:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,swirled the wine a quarter turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.88,0:33:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,set the glass back on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.58,0:33:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,without drinking. What would you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.62,0:33:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,rather it feel like? I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.41,0:33:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,know. I admitted. I'm still
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.14,0:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,figuring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.16,0:33:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He almost smiled. Almost. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.27,0:33:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,at that moment that Renolfo
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.05,0:33:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Saravale crossed the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.64,0:33:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know who he was. I only
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.28,0:33:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,felt the restaurant changed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.66,0:33:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature before he reached
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.15,0:33:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.30,0:33:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,table. Ludovico stiffened half a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.30,0:33:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,degree. Enough for me to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.29,0:33:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough for anyone else to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.10,0:33:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.08,0:33:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo was a man in a light
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.85,0:33:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,suit, a wide smile and heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders, with a colabrian
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.32,0:33:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,accent
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.70,0:33:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that dragged the consonants in a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.07,0:33:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,strange way. Ludovico, what a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.22,0:33:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nice surprise. Renolfo,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.42,0:33:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and this must be the new Mrs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.05,0:34:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Caracciolo. Renolfo turned to me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.85,0:34:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,with theatrical courtesy and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.43,0:34:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,extended
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.88,0:34:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand and immense pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.72,0:34:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I could decide what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.68,0:34:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with my hand, Ludovico simply
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.45,0:34:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,looked
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.82,0:34:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,at him. He didn't speak. He
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.61,0:34:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't move. He just looked. The
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,look lasted exactly the length
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.72,0:34:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of one
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.12,0:34:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,breath and Renolfo understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.91,0:34:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He withdrew his hand with the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.65,0:34:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,smile still hanging on his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.92,0:34:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in the way of a man who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.39,0:34:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,he's lost this round and that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.87,0:34:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the next subject is better left
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.44,0:34:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,untouched. Anyway, Renolfo said
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.66,0:34:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with forced lightness, good to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.81,0:34:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,see you Ludovico, and good night
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.10,0:34:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,man. He left. I kept looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.18,0:34:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico. He went back to his
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.13,0:34:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,glass without comment. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.21,0:34:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.88,0:34:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd learned quickly in that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.44,0:34:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion that asking about a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.00,0:34:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,scene like that was a waste. It
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.79,0:34:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,rained
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.14,0:34:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as we left the restaurant. Not a
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.22,0:34:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,heavy rain. A fine rain. Early
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.17,0:34:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,autumn weather and providence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.68,0:34:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of rain that soaks you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.21,0:34:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,inside without seeming to soak
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.68,0:34:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you. I'd forgotten a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.54,0:34:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico had already opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.12,0:34:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,car door for me when he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.76,0:34:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Without saying a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.14,0:35:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he took off his own coat from
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.63,0:35:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,his shoulders and put it over
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.12,0:35:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,mine. The fabric was warm from
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.66,0:35:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.44,0:35:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It smelled of something woody I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.96,0:35:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't name. He got in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.53,0:35:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,on the driver's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.56,0:35:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion drove in silence. The
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.27,0:35:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,way back to the mansion was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.86,0:35:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,short. The coat weighed on my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.57,0:35:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,back in a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.10,0:35:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,specific way. No one said
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.87,0:35:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. When Bastion parked,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.99,0:35:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico got out, opened my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.91,0:35:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,door,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.70,0:35:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited for me to step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.26,0:35:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He still said nothing. He just
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.83,0:35:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,stood there on the gravel,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.66,0:35:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with the fine rain wetting his
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.11,0:35:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,shirt, waiting for me to pass in
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.65,0:35:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,front so he could close the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.96,0:35:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.48,0:35:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I climbed the entrance stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.93,0:35:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with his coat on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.44,0:35:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion stayed down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.74,0:35:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the upper corridor, I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.43,0:35:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped. Ludovico stopped two
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,steps behind. I took his coat
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.50,0:35:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,off my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.92,0:35:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders very carefully. I held
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.73,0:35:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it back out to him without fully
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.54,0:35:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,raising my eyes. Good night,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.24,0:35:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico. He took the coat by
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.84,0:35:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the shoulders. His thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.16,0:35:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,lingering a second longer than
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.81,0:35:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it needed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.30,0:35:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on the fabric that had touched
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.11,0:35:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,my shoulders. Good night,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.62,0:35:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayolanda. I went into my room. I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.55,0:35:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.90,0:36:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I leaned my back against the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.31,0:36:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wood. I looked at the imaginary
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.88,0:36:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,coat I was no longer wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.34,0:36:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At the sensation of weight that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.33,0:36:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,was still there, stubborn on my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.33,0:36:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. I put my hand to the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.32,0:36:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,collar of my dress and felt my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.03,0:36:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,own pulse at my fingertips,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.57,0:36:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,beating faster than it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.28,0:36:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.74,0:36:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when I understood. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.41,0:36:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,fear of him. It never had been.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.27,0:36:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fear of what was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.64,0:36:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.18,0:36:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to move inside me every time he
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.01,0:36:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet in the right place,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.91,0:36:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the right way, at the right
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.68,0:36:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.34,0:36:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of looking at a coat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.49,0:36:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging on a stranger's arm and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.92,0:36:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking of a woody scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.12,0:36:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of the coffee served
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.52,0:36:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the way I'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.87,0:36:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,drinking it since I was 15,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.98,0:36:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever having told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.39,0:36:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of having cried on the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen floor with a man sitting
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.27,0:36:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,silently
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.66,0:36:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,across from me and discovering
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.70,0:36:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that for two minutes, it was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.61,0:36:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,less lonely than any
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.97,0:36:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.06,0:36:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,had in the last ten years. I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.69,0:36:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned my forehead against the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.45,0:36:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,door. The bell had told for the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.25,0:36:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,last time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.78,0:36:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,two weeks ago. And on the wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.63,0:36:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the corridor, a man I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.47,0:36:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,signed a contract not to love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.20,0:36:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was closing his bedroom door in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.90,0:37:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,silence. At the end of the same
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.61,0:37:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,night he'd covered me with his
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.26,0:37:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,coat in the rain. That was
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.71,0:37:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,where, with my hands still on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.33,0:37:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the handle and my pulse beating
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.06,0:37:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,at my
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.34,0:37:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,collar, I realized I was, for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.30,0:37:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time since the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.46,0:37:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,truly afraid, and the fear had
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.48,0:37:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing to do with debt. Chapter
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.90,0:37:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,four, the shadow returns. Two
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.09,0:37:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks later, I learned that a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.28,0:37:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion sleeps differently from
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.10,0:37:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,normal houses. It doesn't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.92,0:37:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,actually. It slows down. The
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.57,0:37:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,night
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.86,0:37:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,staff moved through the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.06,0:37:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,corridors and silent shoes. The
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.67,0:37:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lighting recedes to a series of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.28,0:37:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,dim
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.44,0:37:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,sconces along the baseboard. And
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the vestibules old clocks keep
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.85,0:37:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,marking time as if no one had
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.44,0:37:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,asked
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.72,0:37:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,their opinion. I had grown used
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.50,0:37:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to crossing that silence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.89,0:37:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,barefoot. In my robe fastened up
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.73,0:37:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to my neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.72,0:37:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when I couldn't sleep. And less
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.77,0:37:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and less could I sleep. That
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.61,0:37:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Monday dawn, I went down to get
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.66,0:37:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a glass of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.32,0:37:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,water. That was the official
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.97,0:37:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,excuse. The real one, I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.86,0:37:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,have the courage to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.40,0:37:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,even to myself. The library
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.21,0:37:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,light was on. A yellow band
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.01,0:37:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,escaped from beneath the half
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.95,0:37:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,open door.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.10,0:38:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped in the corridor with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.87,0:38:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand at the waist of my robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.77,0:38:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could go back. I should go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.42,0:38:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.10,0:38:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I went forward. I pushed the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.82,0:38:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,door with two fingers. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.71,0:38:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was sitting in the tall armchair
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.67,0:38:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,near
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.92,0:38:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the fireplace. His elbows on his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.25,0:38:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,knees, and an untouched glass of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.58,0:38:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,amber in his hand. No tie. No
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.69,0:38:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.20,0:38:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,His white shirt open at the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.53,0:38:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,collar, and the sleeves rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.01,0:38:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the elbow the way he did
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.49,0:38:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when he
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.84,0:38:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,worked outside the office. The
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.65,0:38:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,fire was low. The orange light
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.45,0:38:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,ran across his face and revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.38,0:38:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.62,0:38:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the day's mask hid. The short
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.41,0:38:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,scar at his temple that I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.07,0:38:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,never noticed. The weariness in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.98,0:38:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,his
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.16,0:38:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. The jaw clenched in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.99,0:38:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the way of someone carrying
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.64,0:38:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,something for far too long. He
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.46,0:38:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,raised his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.80,0:38:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't startled. Couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.69,0:38:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep. I came for water. The
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.58,0:38:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchens on the other side. I
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.54,0:38:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,fastened
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.08,0:38:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,robe a little tighter at my
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.42,0:38:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,neck. You couldn't either. He
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,turned the glass slowly between
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.40,0:38:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,his fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.68,0:38:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't drink. He said, looking
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.85,0:38:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at the amber. I just hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.88,0:38:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because if I drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.90,0:39:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I talk too much. We fell silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.14,0:39:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't go in. I went in. I
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.31,0:39:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sat in the armchair across from
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.48,0:39:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,his,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.16,0:39:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with my legs folded to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.97,0:39:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the robe pulled over my
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.49,0:39:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,knees. Neither of us moved for a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.30,0:39:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,while.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire crackled. One of the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.70,0:39:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor clocks struck three in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.42,0:39:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the distance. My brother
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.76,0:39:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,liked this library. He said
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.61,0:39:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly. As if continuing a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.52,0:39:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation we'd never started.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.71,0:39:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.98,0:39:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,read lying there. On the rug, he
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.96,0:39:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,said our father's chair was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.63,0:39:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,uncomfortable on purpose. So no
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.55,0:39:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.74,0:39:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,would think of staying too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.91,0:39:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask the name. I waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.09,0:39:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Enrico. Ludovico kept looking
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.06,0:39:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,at the glass. He was 19 when the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.13,0:39:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,set of all is sent a message in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.13,0:39:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,an alley in the old district. I
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.13,0:39:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.32,0:39:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,only two. My father still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.31,0:39:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was forced to wait six years
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.17,0:39:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could collect that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.85,0:39:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.60,0:39:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to the alley late. I got
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.43,0:39:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there on time with Rennelfo, a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.27,0:39:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,log shifted in the fireplace,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.66,0:39:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and sent a small spark toward
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.24,0:39:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the rug. He looked at the spark,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.98,0:39:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same calm he looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.66,0:40:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,everything else. The spark went
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.74,0:40:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,out on its own. I'm sorry. I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.63,0:40:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,said, and the sentence came out
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.71,0:40:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,low.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.98,0:40:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Without ornament. He nodded.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.84,0:40:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a degree. That was all. I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.83,0:40:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned my forehead against the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.82,0:40:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,back of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.28,0:40:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the armchair. Without planning
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.99,0:40:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to, I started to talk. My mother
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.82,0:40:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ran away from home when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.48,0:40:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.18,0:40:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, with a man in debt. My
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.05,0:40:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,grandmother never forgave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.93,0:40:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She raised me saying that owing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.86,0:40:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,someone was the same as owing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.38,0:40:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself, and that a woman who
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.95,0:40:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on others pays with her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.57,0:40:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,body
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.78,0:40:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sooner or later. I swore from
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the age of ten that I would
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.68,0:40:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,never owe anyone anything. I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.63,0:40:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,raised my
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.82,0:40:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,home. He was watching me with an
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.58,0:40:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,attention that had nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.34,0:40:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with negotiation. Then I sat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.88,0:40:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,down
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.10,0:40:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,across from a man in a cafe and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,signed a contract. I finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.85,0:40:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother would laugh in my
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.81,0:40:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.46,0:40:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico turned the glass once
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.50,0:40:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,more. You don't owe anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.27,0:40:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,anything, Iolanda. I owe $12,000
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.44,0:40:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to someone. You no longer do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.63,0:40:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I owe $12,000 to you. He
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.82,0:41:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned half a degree forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.01,0:41:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His elbows
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.76,0:41:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,still resting on his knees. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.02,0:41:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No? You owe me exactly what I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.13,0:41:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote in the contract. Not one
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.32,0:41:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,comma more. Silence. We stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.07,0:41:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there for another stretch of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.70,0:41:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,time. I couldn't measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.16,0:41:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,touched the other. Neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.70,0:41:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,said anything else of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.86,0:41:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,importance, but something moved
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.58,0:41:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath my ribcage,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.28,0:41:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,something warm, uncomfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.16,0:41:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had come to the library
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,terrified of finding. I stood up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.04,0:41:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,before
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.42,0:41:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it became impossible to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.52,0:41:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night Ludovico. Good night,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.77,0:41:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eolanda. I went to my room. I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.80,0:41:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.22,0:41:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep. But this time the reason
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.03,0:41:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,was different. Tuesday afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.90,0:41:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the mistake I'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.47,0:41:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,putting
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.88,0:41:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,off making. The door to the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.64,0:41:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,small back room next to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.15,0:41:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico's main office stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.04,0:41:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,locked. I'd noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.28,0:41:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,this in the second week. That
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.09,0:41:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon passing through the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.91,0:41:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor, I noticed the door was
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.91,0:41:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a jar,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.28,0:41:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not locked. Dona Ciara had a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.91,0:41:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,headache and Bastion had gone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.61,0:41:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,out with Ludovico to some place
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.42,0:41:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,no one told
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.06,0:41:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,me about. I went in. I should
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.03,0:41:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,have left the same second. I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.94,0:42:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't leave. The small room was
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.11,0:42:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.18,0:42:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,smaller office, full of files,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.36,0:42:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,steel shelves, a side table, an
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.62,0:42:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,open folder left on the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.18,0:42:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten. I went to the table
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.85,0:42:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as if my body had gone before my
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.62,0:42:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,head. I lifted the folder cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The first paper was a photo. A
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.35,0:42:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,delmo. thinner than the last
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.16,0:42:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,time I'd seen him. With a poorly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.24,0:42:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,shaved beard, coming out of a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.93,0:42:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,building that wasn't in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.26,0:42:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence. The photo had a date
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.13,0:42:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.38,0:42:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks after the church bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.18,0:42:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the photo. An address in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.97,0:42:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Newark, New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.70,0:42:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the address. An envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.61,0:42:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,with handwritten notes and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.17,0:42:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,affirmed slanted script. The
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.84,0:42:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,same
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.08,0:42:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as the note that had arrived at
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,my apartment. Is a delmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.31,0:42:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer confirmed. Silence paid
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.72,0:42:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,until
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.10,0:42:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,further notice. I read it three
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.23,0:42:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,times. I didn't understand. I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.23,0:42:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,read it twice more. I understood
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.43,0:42:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,too
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.64,0:42:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,little. That was when I noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.47,0:42:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the step behind me. I turned
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.13,0:42:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. Ludovico was in the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.73,0:42:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.78,0:42:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't huff. He didn't raise
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.42,0:43:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice. He just looked at the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.11,0:43:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,folder in my hand then at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.00,0:43:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Close that door behind you when
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.72,0:43:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you leave. He said, he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.33,0:43:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,say to close it from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.54,0:43:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to close it from the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,outside. I dropped the folder on
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.69,0:43:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the table. My heart beating in
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.26,0:43:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,spot that wasn't my chest. I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.00,0:43:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,left. I passed by him without
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.81,0:43:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,looking. I went to the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.48,0:43:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already crying by the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.05,0:43:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,middle of the stairs. Angry at
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the crying. Angry are still at
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.55,0:43:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.78,0:43:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was feeling beneath the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.21,0:43:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,crying. Over the next few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.03,0:43:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I rehearsed in my head three
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.63,0:43:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,different
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.14,0:43:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,versions of the same sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew where he was from the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.63,0:43:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,start. I knocked on the main
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.26,0:43:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,office door
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.90,0:43:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,two hours later. He told me to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.16,0:43:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,come in. He was standing hands
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.43,0:43:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back of the chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.32,0:43:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.68,0:43:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he knew. You knew where he
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.53,0:43:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,was. I said, I knew. Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.39,0:43:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Since before
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.46,0:43:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you walked into the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.24,0:43:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean? He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.42,0:43:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,answer. Ludovico. Yolanda. What
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.67,0:43:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean? He let the air
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.84,0:43:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,out
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.06,0:43:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,through his nose. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.49,0:44:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,answer properly. He just looked
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.12,0:44:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,at me in a way I couldn't read.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.28,0:44:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew his silence now. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.89,0:44:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to read many silences in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.80,0:44:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that house, but this was a new
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.58,0:44:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.06,0:44:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the silence of the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.65,0:44:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,rule. It was the silence of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.18,0:44:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,someone about to answer and
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.72,0:44:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,choosing the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.40,0:44:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,moment. I didn't wait for the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.28,0:44:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,moment. I became a peace in a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.17,0:44:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,game. I said, my voice coming
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.05,0:44:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,out louder
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.70,0:44:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,than I wanted. A game that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.45,0:44:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,started before I knew I was
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.26,0:44:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,playing. Is that what I became?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.34,0:44:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.88,0:44:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,explain. He looked at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.18,0:44:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.04,0:44:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,explain. Ludovico. I'll tell
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.05,0:44:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.34,0:44:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but not now. When? When I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.97,0:44:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,certain you'll hear me out to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.71,0:44:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the end. I close my eyes for
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.40,0:44:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.60,0:44:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I opened them, I decided
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.10,0:44:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that this mansion wouldn't hold
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.70,0:44:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,me another hour. I left the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.09,0:44:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,office
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.40,0:44:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,without answering. I climbed the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.52,0:44:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. Went into my room. Put a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.64,0:44:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,coat over my dress, grabbed my
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.62,0:44:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.40,0:44:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I went down again. This time
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.98,0:44:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking at any door. I
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.67,0:44:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,passed on a chair in the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.03,0:44:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.00,0:44:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw my face and didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.72,0:45:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the key to the side door
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.45,0:45:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no one used and went out
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.78,0:45:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,through the side gravel path.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.21,0:45:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Going around the mansion so I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.64,0:45:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't pass by the main
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.88,0:45:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.94,0:45:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The service gate opened onto a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.59,0:45:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,narrow lane. I followed the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.34,0:45:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to the street. I followed the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.93,0:45:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,street
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.26,0:45:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to the bus line. I took a bus to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.13,0:45:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the old district without looking
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.00,0:45:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,at anyone's face. I needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.69,0:45:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.46,0:45:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to breathe. I needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.06,0:45:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,remember what it was like to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.47,0:45:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have a body that belonged to no
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.02,0:45:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.48,0:45:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I got off at the stop near the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.32,0:45:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,old market. The one that closes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.22,0:45:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,after six. Wet stone streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.00,0:45:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yellow lamp posts. Few people at
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.38,0:45:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that hour. Merchants gathering
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.60,0:45:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,crates. A loose dog crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.68,0:45:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.86,0:45:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I shoved my hands into my coat
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.45,0:45:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,pockets and walked with no
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.83,0:45:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,destination. The anger pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.47,0:45:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,at
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.58,0:45:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the back of my throat. I passed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.23,0:45:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the closed bakery. Turned on to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.87,0:45:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a cross street that led down to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.52,0:45:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.68,0:45:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,docks. I walked four blocks. It
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.74,0:45:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was at the fifth that I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.86,0:45:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A man in a light suit had
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.52,0:45:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the street at the same
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.15,0:45:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,pace as me. On the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.79,0:45:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he wasn't going anywhere. He was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.53,0:45:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,coming
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.86,0:45:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,toward me. Ranolfo said of Aley.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.77,0:46:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My step froze for half a second
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.61,0:46:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,before I decided to keep walking
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.52,0:46:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with my chin up. He sped up to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.69,0:46:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,intercept me at the corner. He
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.85,0:46:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,got too close. Misses. Caratilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.86,0:46:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He said with the theatrical
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.64,0:46:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,smile. What luck for me? Excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.67,0:46:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,me. I tried to pass. He stepped
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.71,0:46:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.80,0:46:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,cutting off my path without
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.37,0:46:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,touching me. But closing off the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.24,0:46:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,street. It won't take long. I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.93,0:46:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.16,0:46:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted a minute. I don't have a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.18,0:46:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,minute. You do. He tilted his
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.07,0:46:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,head half a degree. The smile
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.95,0:46:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,still
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.28,0:46:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,frozen. One thing I need you to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.37,0:46:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,know. Okay. Your original debt
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.39,0:46:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that one from the wedding. He
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.35,0:46:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,made
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.62,0:46:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a small hand gesture. Like
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.19,0:46:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,someone describing something
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.87,0:46:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,distant. Was with us, Missy. It
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.74,0:46:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.10,0:46:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with the castanzos. The
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.69,0:46:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,castanzos were just the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.77,0:46:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying. I'm not. The smile
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.98,0:46:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.40,0:46:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,move. And we're still waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.19,0:46:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,for payment. In person. The air
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.10,0:46:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,left my lungs all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.16,0:46:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way. Just a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.66,0:46:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,message, Missy's caratilo. He
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:46:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned half a degree. Still
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.02,0:46:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.44,0:46:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,touching me. Tell your husband
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.94,0:47:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that we know where he keeps you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.54,0:47:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him we know where he sent a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.14,0:47:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,delmo. And tell him that time's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.33,0:47:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,running out. Okay. He took a
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.30,0:47:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,step back. He gave a nod. Almost
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.56,0:47:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,courteous. And he was about to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.09,0:47:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,exit the scene when a car
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.36,0:47:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared at the top corner with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.94,0:47:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.30,0:47:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,breaking. The headlight hitting
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.07,0:47:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,him straight in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.50,0:47:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo raised his hand to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.99,0:47:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,shield his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.90,0:47:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion leapt from the driver's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.53,0:47:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,seat with his hand inside his
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.06,0:47:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,coat at the level of the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.32,0:47:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,holster. Get in, ma'am. That was
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.42,0:47:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all he said. Renolfo raised both
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.51,0:47:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hands with theatrical calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.70,0:47:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone who wasn't doing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.06,0:47:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,anything wrong. He stepped back
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.51,0:47:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,two paces into the shadow of the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.01,0:47:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.88,0:47:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared into an alley
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.26,0:47:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,before Bastion could take
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.50,0:47:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,another step. I got into the car
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.08,0:47:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with legs
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.52,0:47:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that were no longer entirely
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.15,0:47:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,mine. Bastion slammed the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.96,0:47:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned the car onto the cross
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.83,0:47:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,street.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.24,0:47:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He accelerated enough to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.79,0:47:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the old district in less than
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.28,0:47:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,three minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.58,0:47:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,without speaking to me. Only
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.90,0:47:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when we got onto the road
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.08,0:47:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,climbing to the upper
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.07,0:47:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood did he
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.96,0:47:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,look at the rear view mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.71,0:47:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, ma'am? I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.45,0:48:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,fine. You don't look it. I ran
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.26,0:48:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.68,0:48:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,over my face. Bastion. Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.84,0:48:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find me? He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.08,0:48:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,answer for half a block. Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.16,0:48:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luda
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.46,0:48:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Vico asked someone to never lose
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.59,0:48:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sight of you. Never. Since the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.58,0:48:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,day of the cafe, you follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.64,0:48:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We look out for you. It's not
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.67,0:48:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the same thing. It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.42,0:48:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion looked ahead. But in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.38,0:48:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.32,0:48:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it worked out to be similar. I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.01,0:48:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet the rest of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.58,0:48:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,way. My face turned to the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.04,0:48:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,window
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.38,0:48:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and a mixture of things in my
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.90,0:48:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,throat that I couldn't separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.58,0:48:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger at having been followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.82,0:48:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Relief at having been followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.97,0:48:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame at both. Renolfo had said
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.13,0:48:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,two sentences that were already
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.28,0:48:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,burying themselves in the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.04,0:48:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,spot where they'd hurt later.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.70,0:48:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your original debt was with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.46,0:48:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your husband that we know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.08,0:48:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,where he keeps you. Bastions had
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.82,0:48:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,one last sentence before we
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.28,0:48:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,parked on the gravel. Mr. Luda
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.06,0:48:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vico will want to talk. Better
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.84,0:48:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to let him speak to the end this
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.74,0:48:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.50,0:48:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't answer. I got out of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.21,0:48:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the car. I climbed the three
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.87,0:48:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,steps of the entrance. The main
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.70,0:48:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,door
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.94,0:49:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was already open. Luda Vico was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.18,0:49:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the foot of the stairs. No
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.28,0:49:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket. No tie. His sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.23,0:49:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,still rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.10,0:49:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,up at the elbow the way they
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.78,0:49:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,were in the library. He wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.58,0:49:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,angry. He was something worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.38,0:49:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.28,0:49:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and Luda Vico, Karachiolo
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.04,0:49:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid, with something all of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.09,0:49:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence had never seen. And
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.20,0:49:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.62,0:49:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,without meaning to, saw. He had
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.37,0:49:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a folder in his hand. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.13,0:49:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the folder from the back office.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.40,0:49:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was another folder. Thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.02,0:49:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Heldunder his arm with a car
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.49,0:49:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that didn't match the rest of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.01,0:49:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.94,0:49:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He lowered his chin half a
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.42,0:49:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,degree. He looked at me. And for
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.24,0:49:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time since the cafe,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.48,0:49:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice came out without any
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.27,0:49:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,mask. Sit. I'm going to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.18,0:49:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.84,0:49:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 5 The Truth Without a
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.87,0:49:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Contract. The folder under his
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.97,0:49:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,arm was too thick. I recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.14,0:49:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the worn leather from far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.88,0:49:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The same color as the one I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.56,0:49:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,seen in the back room. Tuesday
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.30,0:49:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.48,0:49:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with the photo of a delmo and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.06,0:49:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Newark inside. Luda Vico was at
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.75,0:49:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the foot of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.50,0:49:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As Bastion had worn in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.46,0:50:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was no mask at all on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.42,0:50:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,his face. Only weariness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.60,0:50:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And something deeper that I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.92,0:50:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't name. And that squeezed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.48,0:50:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my chest before I could defend
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.94,0:50:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.28,0:50:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit. He said, low. When I came
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.50,0:50:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in through the door. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.65,0:50:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,obey at first. I stood there
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.72,0:50:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with my coat wet from the old
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.21,0:50:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,district's drizzle stuck to my
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.75,0:50:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. Still tasting the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.19,0:50:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,metallic
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.60,0:50:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,taste that the scare with
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.00,0:50:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo had left in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.62,0:50:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion came in behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.36,0:50:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looked at his boss. Looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.97,0:50:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,me. And disappeared down the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.52,0:50:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen corridor without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.80,0:50:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let you out. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.98,0:50:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,appear. The mansion seemed to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.25,0:50:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,have agreed with her to hold its
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.65,0:50:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.96,0:50:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit, Elanda. Please. The please
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.23,0:50:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,was what moved me. I'd never
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.27,0:50:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,heard that word from his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.02,0:50:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat in one of the library arm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.53,0:50:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,chairs where he guided me. And
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.99,0:50:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he pulled the other one and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.30,0:50:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,turned it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.74,0:50:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to face me. So close our knees
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.51,0:50:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,almost touched. He said the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.11,0:50:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,folder on the little table
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.65,0:50:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.52,0:50:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't open it. What I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.26,0:50:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,about to tell you. You've had
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.13,0:50:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the right to know for weeks. You
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.19,0:50:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,began.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.08,0:50:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice horser than it usually
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.80,0:51:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was. I put it off because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.46,0:51:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid you'd get up and leave
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.02,0:51:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,before the end. Today, if you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.19,0:51:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,get up, you get up. I won't hold
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.58,0:51:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you. My jaw locked. I made a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.67,0:51:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,small
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.04,0:51:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture with my head for him to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.86,0:51:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,go on. Ludovico opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.39,0:51:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,folder and took out three
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.85,0:51:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,sheets. He
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.44,0:51:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't look at them. Adelmo owed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.57,0:51:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the cerevaules. He said, he owed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.70,0:51:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,them for over a year. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.76,0:51:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,gambling. It wasn't an end of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.41,0:51:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the month vise. He got into a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.07,0:51:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,deal with Renolfo thinking he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.83,0:51:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,come
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.06,0:51:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,out rich and came out owing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.56,0:51:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,35,000 dollars. And a promise he
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.35,0:51:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't have the courage to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.07,0:51:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.24,0:51:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,about. Adelmo's name and his
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.88,0:51:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth sounded distant. As if he
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.69,0:51:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,were speaking of a man I'd known
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.56,0:51:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.68,0:51:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,another life. Maybe he was. The
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.98,0:51:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,promise was you. He continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.21,0:51:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes fixed on mine. The deal
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.58,0:51:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,between Adelmo and the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.71,0:51:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,collaborate in clan was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.30,0:51:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On the wedding day, the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.48,0:51:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,cerevaules would appear
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.66,0:51:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,at the church. Adelmo would sign
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.44,0:51:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever he needed to sign and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.10,0:51:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,disappear through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.88,0:51:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd leave with them. His debt
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.87,0:51:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,would be forgiven. You'd be the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.86,0:52:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,payment in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.58,0:52:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Something inside me went cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.61,0:52:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way that left no tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.56,0:52:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Only silence. I clashed my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.72,0:52:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in my
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.06,0:52:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,lap so I wouldn't move. The
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.94,0:52:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wedding debt. He said, was built
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.17,0:52:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of that. The custonzo
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.12,0:52:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.68,0:52:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,have been a front for the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.01,0:52:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,cerevaules for three years. They
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.71,0:52:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,collected your signature in the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.36,0:52:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,middle of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.84,0:52:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the venue papers because they
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.11,0:52:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,needed a rope around your neck
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.42,0:52:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in case the church plan failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.78,0:52:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Two traps for the same day. One
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.76,0:52:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to walk in wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.42,0:52:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,white. Another so you'd have
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.20,0:52:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nowhere to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.84,0:52:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,run if the white dress wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.59,0:52:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,enough. How did you find out? I
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.47,0:52:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,said, and my voice came out
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.10,0:52:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,steady,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.08,0:52:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which surprised me. Three days
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.80,0:52:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,before the wedding. My lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.47,0:52:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has an old informant in the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.02,0:52:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,custonzo's
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.60,0:52:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,accounting. Bousto Renieri,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.30,0:52:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll meet him. The name
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.87,0:52:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed his desk by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.34,0:52:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Link to Renolfo, Link to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.18,0:52:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought it to me that same
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.91,0:52:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,night. He stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.98,0:52:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ren is hand over his face. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.97,0:52:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,continued. I went after a delmo
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.96,0:52:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that same early morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.94,0:52:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught him at his place. With
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.61,0:53:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a bag packed for another city,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.23,0:53:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't the one he told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.24,0:53:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He confessed everything in 20
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.03,0:53:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes. He cried. He begged
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.77,0:53:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness from the wall, not
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.62,0:53:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him two options. He
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.93,0:53:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears from Providence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.44,0:53:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,before dawn, with enough money
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.18,0:53:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.64,0:53:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Newark and live quietly. Or I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.31,0:53:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,let the cerevaules find out he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.16,0:53:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to escape the deal. He
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.77,0:53:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,chose
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.06,0:53:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Newark before I finished the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.74,0:53:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence. I closed my eyes. I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.48,0:53:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,saw a delmo at the church in his
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.40,0:53:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.04,0:53:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,smiling for photos the week
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.67,0:53:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,before. I saw the church bell
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.42,0:53:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,tolling 12 times. I opened them
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.30,0:53:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.12,0:53:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You made him abandon me at the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.76,0:53:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,altar. I made him abandon you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.34,0:53:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,before he sold you. The
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.60,0:53:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,distinction
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.20,0:53:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,landed between us like an open
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.84,0:53:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,blade. It didn't hurt me the way
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.60,0:53:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it should have hurt. It just
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.13,0:53:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.46,0:53:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there gleaming. The bell, I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.60,0:53:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,said. And the bell returned
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.74,0:53:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,inside my head. Tolling slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.20,0:53:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you let the bell toll. I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.75,0:53:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't stop the bell without
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.68,0:53:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,stopping the town. If I'd shown
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.68,0:53:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,up at
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.00,0:53:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the church pulling you away by
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.61,0:53:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the arm, the cerevaules would
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.16,0:53:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,know within two hours that I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.77,0:53:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,stepped in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.64,0:54:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd become a double target and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.51,0:54:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd become a war. I let the bell
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.39,0:54:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,toll because humiliation passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.94,0:54:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet doesn't. I swallowed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.07,0:54:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hard. My mouth was dry in a
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.93,0:54:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,strange way. The next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.98,0:54:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he said. I bought the costanzo's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.25,0:54:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,debt. I paid the $12,000 in your
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.52,0:54:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,name plus the rest the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.08,0:54:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,devils expected to receive on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.05,0:54:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the side. Two hours later, I had
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.22,0:54:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the paper in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.42,0:54:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer owed anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.70,0:54:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. Except you didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.35,0:54:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that. And I couldn't come
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.63,0:54:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.40,0:54:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,without the cerevaules
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.47,0:54:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding that their
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.63,0:54:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,merchandise had a new owner. So
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.13,0:54:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you waited for me to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.10,0:54:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,lose my job. My apartment, my
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.97,0:54:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,name. I waited for you to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.90,0:54:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that still tied you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.83,0:54:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.22,0:54:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,town. He said. And his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.97,0:54:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,finally wavered. Because if I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.91,0:54:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked on your door with money
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.84,0:54:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.97,0:54:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd throw it in my face. If
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.97,0:54:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd knocked on your door on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.83,0:54:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday with you already
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.62,0:54:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,having
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.03,0:54:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,nowhere to go, you'd listen to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.12,0:54:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,me. I played you. I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.86,0:54:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend I didn't. The silence
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.88,0:54:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.11,0:55:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard my own pulse in my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.06,0:55:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The contract. I said. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.07,0:55:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,only way I saw to have you under
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.08,0:55:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.33,0:55:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,roof without the cerevaules
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.89,0:55:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding what it was. If
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.56,0:55:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you became my wife on paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.71,0:55:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you became untouchable in
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.05,0:55:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence. No one touches the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.66,0:55:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don's wife without starting a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.22,0:55:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,war.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.43,0:55:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to start. The whole
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.79,0:55:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,coldness, the separate rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.93,0:55:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the rules, the no questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.57,0:55:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was to give you space, not to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.21,0:55:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,control you. I didn't know how
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.90,0:55:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to offer you protection without
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.66,0:55:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.77,0:55:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,looking like a prison. I chose
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.88,0:55:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong. I chose too cold. I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.70,0:55:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed quiet. He waited. He
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.60,0:55:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't try to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.51,0:55:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,fill it. And a delmo? I said
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.45,0:55:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,afterward. The photo in Newark.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.60,0:55:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I pay a man to keep an eye on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.61,0:55:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.17,0:55:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because I care about a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.37,0:55:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,delmo. Because as long as he's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.76,0:55:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,alive in some corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.73,0:55:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the cerevaules think the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.08,0:55:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,original deal can still be
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.53,0:55:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,collected. The day he decides to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.33,0:55:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,come back
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.83,0:55:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to Providence thinking he can
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.39,0:55:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,turn the tables. I need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.06,0:55:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,before he does. That's what that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.79,0:55:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,note meant. Silence paid. His
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.97,0:55:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,silence. Not mine with you. I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.15,0:56:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,stood up. I didn't know where I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.48,0:56:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.63,0:56:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I only knew I couldn't stay
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.08,0:56:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting. I walked to the library
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.79,0:56:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,window, leaned my forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.18,0:56:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,against the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.77,0:56:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,glass, and looked at the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.46,0:56:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,garden. His reflection appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.27,0:56:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,behind mine in the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.73,0:56:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seated. Still. Waiting. I need
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.48,0:56:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,air. I said, go. I left the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.96,0:56:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,library with a firm step,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.63,0:56:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and went down the corridor to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.15,0:56:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the back of a randa. The drizzle
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.82,0:56:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,had stopped. The winter garden
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.39,0:56:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.55,0:56:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,its light low, and the veranda
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.18,0:56:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was empty. I leaned against the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.87,0:56:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,iron railing and breathed deeply
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.61,0:56:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first time in an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.66,0:56:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I cried. I didn't cry
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.70,0:56:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,over a delmo. I cried over the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.75,0:56:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks I'd slept in that room
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.11,0:56:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking I was merchandise. I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.52,0:56:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,cried over the church bell
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.79,0:56:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,holding 12 times, knowing now
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.49,0:56:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that behind that bell there had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.30,0:56:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,been a plan to hand me over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.88,0:56:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,behind
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.23,0:56:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a cabinet. I cried over the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.82,0:56:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,glass of water he'd set beside
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.59,0:56:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my knee in the kitchen weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.23,0:56:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.89,0:56:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and that I'd seen at the time as
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.78,0:56:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,elegant coldness. And now saw as
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.67,0:56:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing he knew how to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.39,0:56:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,do without frightening me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.22,0:57:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,cried because I'd spent weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.11,0:57:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking I was his shield when
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.07,0:57:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.53,0:57:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,he was the one who had become
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.42,0:57:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,mine. He didn't come after me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.50,0:57:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there until the sky went
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.51,0:57:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,fully dark. When I went back to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.38,0:57:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the library, he was still
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.90,0:57:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting in the same armchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.65,0:57:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.83,0:57:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,folder closed on the little
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.56,0:57:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,table. His hands and his lap
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.36,0:57:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,intertwined. You should have
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.16,0:57:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.91,0:57:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I said from the doorway. I was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.65,0:57:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,going to tell you when you no
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.33,0:57:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,longer needed me. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.17,0:57:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,without raising his eyes, that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.11,0:57:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence landed in a strange
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.92,0:57:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,way. I stood there absorbing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.21,0:57:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pride, Ludovico. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.34,0:57:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,low. That's fear with a pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.39,0:57:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,name. He raised his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.11,0:57:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look away. It is. He
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.52,0:57:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,said, I know. I sat back down in
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.10,0:57:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the armchair across from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.71,0:57:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him for a stretch of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.62,0:57:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,time. I didn't measure. He
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.16,0:57:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't rush me. Tomorrow, I
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.77,0:57:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.55,0:57:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,finally, I want the three elders
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.74,0:57:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,here. In this hall, I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.92,0:57:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,speak with them. I
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.15,0:57:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,alanda, I'm calling them. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.04,0:58:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you. They called me a bot bride
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.07,0:58:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,behind my back. I want them to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.03,0:58:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,hear
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.29,0:58:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,me face to face. He was silent
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.30,0:58:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,for a few seconds. Then he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.45,0:58:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow night. Tomorrow night,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.91,0:58:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood up and went up the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.27,0:58:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs slowly. I didn't go to my
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.93,0:58:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,room. I walked to the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.60,0:58:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.81,0:58:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. Stoped at the door I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.69,0:58:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,never opened. And went back to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.45,0:58:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my room because it wasn't yet
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.16,0:58:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.77,0:58:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I knew it was a matter of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.51,0:58:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,hours. I slept little. I dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.43,0:58:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the church bell
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.51,0:58:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,tolding 12 times. And of his
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.35,0:58:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,hand setting a glass of water
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.25,0:58:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,beside my knee. The next night,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.29,0:58:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the main hall was lit as if for
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.25,0:58:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a family dinner. And it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.21,0:58:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The three elders arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.73,0:58:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes apart from each
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.31,0:58:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,other. Don Vittario came first,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.20,0:58:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,tall and thin, with a silk scarf
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.14,0:58:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,inside
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.51,0:58:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is overcoat. Don Emilliano next,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.81,0:58:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,stalky, with the crest of the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.90,0:58:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,split crown lion on his pinky
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.99,0:58:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ring,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.57,0:58:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and an unlit cigarette between
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.57,0:58:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,his fingers. Don C. Sto last,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.51,0:58:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,bent by the years, with a silver
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.65,0:58:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,handleed cane. The family
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.26,0:58:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,lawyer, Fausto Renieri, the same
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.31,0:59:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,one Lutavico had mentioned in
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.18,0:59:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.73,0:59:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived alongside the hardest of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.27,0:59:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the three, and stood leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.61,0:59:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,against one of the columns.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.81,0:59:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Silent, Bastion stayed at the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.36,0:59:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,door. Lutavico waited on the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.86,0:59:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,other side of the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.39,0:59:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,without interfering. I came down
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.13,0:59:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the stairs and the dark blue
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.65,0:59:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,dress Donacciara had laid on the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.39,0:59:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,bed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.55,0:59:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,for me without asking. I stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.26,0:59:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the hall. The
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.87,0:59:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,three elders looked at me the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.42,0:59:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,way you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.79,0:59:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,look at an expensive piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.71,0:59:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,China, assessing whether it's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.64,0:59:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,cracked. Gentlemen, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.93,0:59:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and my voice came out steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.55,0:59:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of you, at some point
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.28,0:59:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the last month, called me a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.96,0:59:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,bride,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.57,0:59:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,bought in some corner of this
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.07,0:59:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,house. I know this because this
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.67,0:59:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,house is large but not large
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.12,0:59:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,enough
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.43,0:59:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for a whisper not to climb the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.63,0:59:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. Girl, Don C. Sto began,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.91,0:59:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice rasping. This is not
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.11,0:59:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.33,0:59:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,place for, I raised my hand. Let
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.63,0:59:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,me finish. I was bought, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.72,0:59:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you're right about that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.15,0:59:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're getting wrong is
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.70,0:59:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about the merchandise. The
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.20,0:59:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,merchandise wasn't me. It was my
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.04,0:59:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,life,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.59,1:00:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and whoever paid for it paid so
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.12,1:00:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that it wouldn't be taken from
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.59,1:00:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,me by another clan. You know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.97,1:00:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which clan.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.97,1:00:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know by whom. I saw Don
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.75,1:00:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Emiliano exchange a look with
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.67,1:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Vittorio. I continued. I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.51,1:00:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.91,1:00:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,come here to ask you to like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.89,1:00:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of my concern. I came
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.81,1:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to say only one thing. I chose
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.67,1:00:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay. Not because of the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.31,1:00:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,contract. The contract still has
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.26,1:00:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,almost a year to go, and you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.97,1:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.21,1:00:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,better than anyone that paper
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.22,1:00:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,tears. I stay because I chose
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.23,1:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to. No clause, no exit door, no
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.37,1:00:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,price.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.33,1:00:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My gaze crossed Ludovico's from
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.97,1:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the other side of the hall. He
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.56,1:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,understood I was speaking to him
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.26,1:00:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,too.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.79,1:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand closed slowly around
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.22,1:00:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,his own wrist. In the place
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.55,1:00:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,where he wore his father's
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.83,1:00:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.65,1:00:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all. I said to the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.29,1:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,elders, good night. I turned and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.40,1:00:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,went up the stairs. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.24,1:00:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,look back
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.83,1:00:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to know whether he was coming. I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.44,1:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,knew he was. He caught up with
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.94,1:00:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,me in the middle of the upper
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.40,1:00:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.47,1:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't speak. I walked three
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.86,1:00:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,more steps and stopped in front
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.25,1:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of the door at the end of the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.55,1:00:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.73,1:00:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. His mind was three
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.72,1:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,doors back, on the right. He
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.70,1:01:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped behind me. So close I
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.76,1:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,felt his breath in my
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.25,1:01:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hair. I turned slowly. His eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.24,1:01:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,were dark in a new way, and his
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.22,1:01:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hand rose until it almost
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.82,1:01:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,touched
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.27,1:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,my face and stopped in the air,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.25,1:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting. I took his hand and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.04,1:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed it to my face myself. He
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.09,1:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,led out his breath like someone
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.72,1:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd been holding it for
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.03,1:01:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,months. Chapter six, the door
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.56,1:01:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.77,1:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,closes, the morning that dawns.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.59,1:01:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand was warm on my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.32,1:01:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine over his,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.91,1:01:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,trembled for half a
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.83,1:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,second and stopped. If you come
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.85,1:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in here, he said, low, his eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.88,1:01:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,on mine. There's no more
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.45,1:01:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,contract
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.97,1:01:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,between us. Good. I said, he
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.98,1:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned his forehead against
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.92,1:01:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,mine. We stayed there, breathing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.22,1:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the same
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.79,1:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,air of the corridor. The sounds
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.52,1:01:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of the house switched off below.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.32,1:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The elders already leaving
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.77,1:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,without my seeing. The whole
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.44,1:01:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion seeming to know that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.11,1:01:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this instant was ours alone. The
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.01,1:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.49,1:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was dark except for the yellow
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.02,1:01:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,light of the sconce at the end
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.55,1:01:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of the wall. And that light
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.93,1:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,rested on
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.39,1:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,his face in a way I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.90,1:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,have had the courage to describe
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.62,1:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,aloud. Then he kissed me. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.35,1:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,just one kiss. Slow, long,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.24,1:02:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,quiet, like someone finally
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.21,1:02:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,saying a sentence he'd rehearsed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.54,1:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.27,1:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And discovered was simpler than
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.26,1:02:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd imagined. His hands slid
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.12,1:02:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,down to my waist and stayed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.85,1:02:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.17,1:02:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with a firmness that wasn't
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.81,1:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,urgency. It was decision. Mine
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.63,1:02:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,rose to the nape of his neck,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.81,1:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the door at the end of the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.74,1:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,left corridor opened behind him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.80,1:02:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in. The door closed. I
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.67,1:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,woke
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.93,1:02:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with sun on my face and didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.47,1:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it first where I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.12,1:02:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The window was different.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.95,1:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Larger, facing the side garden
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.67,1:02:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen from that angle.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.45,1:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The curtains were heavy linen.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.17,1:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The color of sand. Not the light
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.20,1:02:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,white ones of my room. The smell
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.23,1:02:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the air was different, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.41,1:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark wood, something citrusy and
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.10,1:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,clean that I'd already learned
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.69,1:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to associate with him without
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.23,1:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing when I'd learned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.20,1:02:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a hand on my back,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.31,1:02:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,broad, warm, resting on my spine
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.41,1:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with the calm of someone who
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.95,1:02:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't intend to leave anytime
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.60,1:02:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,soon. I turned slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.47,1:02:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovica was awake, propped on
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.17,1:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,his elbow. Looking at me the way
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.99,1:03:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a person looks when they finally
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.81,1:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,allowed themselves to look,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.65,1:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,without controlling, without
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.55,1:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,calculating. Just looking. As if
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.73,1:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I were a
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.27,1:03:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,problem he'd given up solving
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.03,1:03:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided simply to have. Good
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.98,1:03:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. He said,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.51,1:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice horse from morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.19,1:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,deeper than usual. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.04,1:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran his thumb over the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.89,1:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.01,1:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,my mouth. I don't know what he
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.49,1:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was checking, but he did it with
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.06,1:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the attention of someone
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.25,1:03:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,verifying
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.69,1:03:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that something is still real.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.41,1:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Half a laugh of mine escaped
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.06,1:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,before I decided to let it. What
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.96,1:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.31,1:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to remember the name
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.36,1:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of my room. I said, I think I
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.29,1:03:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,forgot. He laughed low.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.21,1:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a sound I'd heard very
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.91,1:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,few times. And that, that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.38,1:03:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,morning, seemed to open
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.73,1:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,something in his
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.67,1:03:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,chest. Something he'd kept
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.19,1:03:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,closed for a long time. And now
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.00,1:03:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,let out through that small
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.52,1:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,crack.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.37,1:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a knock at the door
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.30,1:03:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with two discrete taps. Donut
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.22,1:03:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yara's voice from outside,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.45,1:03:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the wood with the same
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.17,1:03:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,professional serenity as always.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.99,1:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee sir and madam. The tray
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.71,1:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is out here when you want it. I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.20,1:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,heard the sound of her footsteps
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.74,1:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,moving away down the corridor,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.81,1:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with a short pause at the end
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.42,1:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,before she disappeared. Exactly
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.14,1:04:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the length of a contained smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.43,1:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculated not to be heard and
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.24,1:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,completely audible anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.80,1:04:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico got up, put on his
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.43,1:04:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,white shirt
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.09,1:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,without buttoning it, went to
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.73,1:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the door and came back with the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.48,1:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,tray. Two fine porcelain cups,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.81,1:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a saucer with thin biscuits, and
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.77,1:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,my cup already set with two
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.42,1:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,cubes in a drop of milk. I put
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.25,1:04:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,both hands around it and said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.74,1:04:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. The warmth passed
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.07,1:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,through the porcelain and warmed
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.71,1:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.81,1:04:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,palms. He saw that I saw. She
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.80,1:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,knows that I know. He said,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.64,1:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting again on the edge of the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.84,1:04:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.53,1:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I left it noted on the first
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.20,1:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,day. I know you did. We drank
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.94,1:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee without hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.89,1:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the window of his room,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.64,1:04:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the side garden appeared whole.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.39,1:04:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The hedges still with due caught
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.20,1:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.31,1:04:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the leaves. The morning light
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,cutting through everything at a
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.61,1:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,diagonal. It was a different
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.15,1:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,view
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.37,1:04:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,from the one in my room. More
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.20,1:04:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,open. Deeper. I thought it would
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.21,1:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,take me a while to get used to
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.10,1:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.57,1:05:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I realized I was getting
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.04,1:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,used to it now. We went down
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.47,1:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,together afterward.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.03,1:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion was crossing the hall
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.45,1:05:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with a folder under his arm, and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.02,1:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the sure step of someone who has
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.59,1:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,three tasks to solve before 10
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.26,1:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in the morning. When he saw us
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.93,1:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,come down side by side on the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.54,1:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.41,1:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,he stopped for a third of a
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.81,1:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,second. The corner of his eye
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.32,1:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,betrayed half a millimeter of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.83,1:05:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,curiosity,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.35,1:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and he kept walking toward the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.05,1:05:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,library without breaking his
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.64,1:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,step. I thought I was going to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.35,1:05:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.27,1:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I held it. Dona Kiarra passed us
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.10,1:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen corridor,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.47,1:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying a basket of flowers cut
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.30,1:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.53,1:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the garden. White hydranges and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.41,1:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,sprigs of rosemary and said,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.11,1:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,good morning, sir, and madam,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.41,1:05:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same neutral intonation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.01,1:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as always, except for the corner
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.61,1:05:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of her mouth that was making
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.01,1:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a visible and silent effort to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.82,1:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,stay still. Ludovico squeezed my
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.76,1:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,hand inside his more firmly.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.45,1:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingers enter lacing mine,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.31,1:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and made no comment. We
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.74,1:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,continued down the corridor
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.41,1:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.03,1:05:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,garden as if coming down the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.26,1:05:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs together on a Saturday
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.53,1:05:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,morning where the most natural
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.84,1:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,thing in the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.37,1:05:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,world. Maybe it already was.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.40,1:06:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside, the day had dawned
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.36,1:06:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,clear, with that firm winter
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.40,1:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,blue that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.05,1:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,promises no warmth but delivers
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.71,1:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,light to spare. The leaves still
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.42,1:06:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,wet from the previous night's
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.98,1:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,drizzle
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.35,1:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,glistened. The air smelled of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.05,1:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,damp earth, and the thin smoke
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.82,1:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of coffee rising from the open
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.58,1:06:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.05,1:06:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He led me to the stone bench
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.03,1:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath the Magnolia. Sat pulled
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.30,1:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,me to sit beside him,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.97,1:06:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept my hand inside his on
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.29,1:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,his knee. No tie, no audience,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.60,1:06:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no contract. Just the hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.99,1:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and the cold bench beneath us,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.51,1:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the light hitting the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.77,1:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnolia leaves that still had
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.29,1:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,late blossoms
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.95,1:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,high in the branches. It's the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.84,1:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,first time I said low, that I
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,hold you in public without it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.48,1:06:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,being for
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.05,1:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,appearances. Yes, he didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.91,1:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,answer. He just squeezed gently.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.12,1:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,His thumb passing over my
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.84,1:06:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,knuckles once.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.23,1:06:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed there a good while,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.72,1:06:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing to fill it. A
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.21,1:06:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,swallow landed on the edge of
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.69,1:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone fountain,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.09,1:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,drank, and flew away. The
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.41,1:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion's kitchen led out the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.95,1:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,smell of hot bread through the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.53,1:06:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,open window.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.75,1:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something in my chest, which I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.34,1:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,been carrying clenched since the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.93,1:07:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,church bell,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.01,1:07:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,since the collector days of the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.57,1:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,door. Since the afternoon I
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.94,1:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,signed a contract just to have
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.45,1:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere to sleep, began to
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.62,1:07:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,loosen slowly, not all at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.01,1:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly, like a knot that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.87,1:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,eased after being tied too tight
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.71,1:07:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for too long. Bastion came up
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.38,1:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone path with a firmer
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.99,1:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,step than usual. He had an
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.68,1:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope in his hand. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.62,1:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,raised his head, and I saw the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.57,1:07:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,exact
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.89,1:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,moment he saw the envelope. His
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.09,1:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,body changed. Not much, just in
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.30,1:07:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the shoulders, in the line of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.36,1:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,his jaw,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.93,1:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way of straightening his
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.81,1:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,spine that wasn't posture. It
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.68,1:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was alertness. It just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.39,1:07:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion said, handing the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.21,1:07:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope into his hand. Man on a
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.54,1:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,motorcycle didn't stop. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.87,1:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,turned the envelope over. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.78,1:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,old. The darkened cream color of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.70,1:07:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,something that had spent time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.43,1:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,kept in a drawer or a safe. And
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.38,1:07:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back there was a red wax
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.34,1:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,seal with the split crown
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.91,1:07:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,lion crest stamped deep and with
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.17,1:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,precision. The same crest is the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.43,1:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder's Rings. The same as
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.27,1:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the Manchins main gate. Except
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.06,1:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that seal seemed older than the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.92,1:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rings. Older than the library's
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.77,1:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,dark wood. Older than anything
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.45,1:08:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd touched in that house. He
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.07,1:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the crest for two
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.58,1:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.97,1:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,longer than he should have. The
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.63,1:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,garden was quiet. The swallow
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.19,1:08:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,came back to the fountain and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.75,1:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,flew away
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.23,1:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,again. Then he closed his hand
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.11,1:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,around the envelope carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.98,1:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Bastion. Bastion
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.67,1:08:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,nodded and went back up the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.20,1:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,stone path with nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.84,1:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico stood up. I'll be right
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.65,1:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.31,1:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed him with my eyes down
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.98,1:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the covered corridor to the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.39,1:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,office. The door closed with a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.96,1:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,soft
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.17,1:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,click. I sat on the bench. My
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.11,1:08:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,hand marked by the warmth of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.99,1:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,his. Watching the swallow land
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.00,1:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.47,1:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,third time on the edge of the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.05,1:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,fountain. I mentally counted the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.79,1:08:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds without meaning to
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.20,1:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,count. He
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.69,1:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,came back at 42, without the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.50,1:08:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope. With his hands in his
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.49,1:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,pockets, his shoulders slightly
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.49,1:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.01,1:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His face composed back into the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.88,1:08:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,expression I'd learned to read
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.68,1:08:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath. He sat again beside me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.83,1:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He took my hand again. Firmer
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.55,1:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,this time. Two firm for a
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.04,1:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Saturday morning that until a
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.76,1:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,minute ago
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.35,1:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,had been going very well. What
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.16,1:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,was it? I asked low. Nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.84,1:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that needs to reach you today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.17,1:09:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him. He held my gaze
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.15,1:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking away. And I saw
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.06,1:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,both things at once. The truth
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.91,1:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about it not being today. And
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.74,1:09:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the lie about it being nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.69,1:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two distinct things. Living in
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.58,1:09:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.77,1:09:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,same sentence. In the same dark
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.73,1:09:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes I'd already learned not to
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.70,1:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,underestimate. I could ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.93,1:09:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I could insist. I could get up
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.48,1:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from there and go to the office
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.08,1:09:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,drawer and open the envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.53,1:09:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.27,1:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that this house's door was
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.17,1:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,mine, too. I had that right. I
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.08,1:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't. I chose to stay at
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.73,1:09:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,peace for one morning. A whole
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.69,1:09:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. Without a knot in my
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.59,1:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,chest. Without a collector.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.35,1:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a bell.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.79,1:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd earned the right to choose
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.65,1:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this. All right. I said, he
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.32,1:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,squeezed my hand again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.75,1:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he relaxed his grip. And we
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.82,1:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there a while longer. On
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.82,1:09:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the bench. Benete the Magnollia.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.41,1:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With the smell of the kitchen's
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.86,1:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,bread arriving through the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.07,1:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,window. And the swallow coming
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.47,1:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,back a
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.75,1:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,fourth time as if it too were in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.52,1:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,no hurry to go anywhere. We went
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.28,1:10:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to the winter garden late in the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.05,1:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. He brought a book. I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.96,1:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,brought another. The space was
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.93,1:10:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,made of glass and iron. Full of
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.97,1:10:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,plants
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.37,1:10:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,don't a GR attended with an
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.81,1:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,attention I'd never seen
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.09,1:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,dedicated to plants. And the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.58,1:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,light came in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.27,1:10:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,from every side at once. Warm
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.17,1:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and diffuse even in winter. I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.07,1:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on the long sofa near the
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.97,1:10:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,largest pain where the sun hit
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.96,1:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,hardest. He sat in the armchair
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.02,1:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,beside me. Stretched out his
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.88,1:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hand
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.15,1:10:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking and rested his
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.92,1:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers on my ankle. The gesture
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.80,1:10:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer asked permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.01,1:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't take his hand away. I
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.86,1:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,read two pages without
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.17,1:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding anything. I reread
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.07,1:10:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.63,1:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood. The light came in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.18,1:10:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,through the pains and fell on
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.63,1:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the broad leaves of the plants
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.13,1:10:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.23,1:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,bleak, slow bands. And I thought
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.25,1:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,without meaning to think it that
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.27,1:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd put away that envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.97,1:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,too carefully for it to be
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.50,1:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing. That his hand was too
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.26,1:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,firm to be just a Saturday
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.78,1:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.13,1:10:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I let the thought pass. Not
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.98,1:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because I believed it. Because
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.04,1:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,today his hand was on my ankle.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.63,1:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sun was good. And I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.22,1:11:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,climb the stairs the night
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.65,1:11:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,before without a contract. And
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.29,1:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.51,1:11:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,morning was mine. Tomorrow I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.46,1:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,would ask. Tomorrow if he didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.68,1:11:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me I'd go after it. I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.62,1:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.11,1:11:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,learn to go after things. And
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.71,1:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd already learned that the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.26,1:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,truth doesn't disappear. It only
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.03,1:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,waits. Or today I stayed. Lena
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.42,1:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,here, that wraps up book one.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.72,1:11:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've already finished book
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.11,1:11:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,two.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.61,1:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get access to it for a
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.06,1:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,really small fee. I thought
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.17,1:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest danger of my life
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.88,1:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.05,1:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,been hiring ever and for one
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.07,1:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,night. But I was wrong. The real
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.38,1:11:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,danger began when I started to
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.54,1:11:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,believe
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.05,1:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that by his side I could finally
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.80,1:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,be happy. He loved me without
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.29,1:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,hiding it, protected me without
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.95,1:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,confining me. His arms around me
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.27,1:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,felt like the only safe place in
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.59,1:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.53,1:11:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I found the envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.37,1:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden in his drawer. Three
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.28,1:12:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,photos. My face marked on the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.33,1:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,screen of a
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.11,1:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,news report that hadn't yet
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.74,1:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,aired. A transfer receipt with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.55,1:12:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the exact date of the worst
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.19,1:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,night of my
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.85,1:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,life. And a message from him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.61,1:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Short. Sent to a number I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.66,1:12:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize. She
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.99,1:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,can't find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.17,1:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Within a few hours, my life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.98,1:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,became a headline. The same
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.79,1:12:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,people who'd applauded me now
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.73,1:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.53,1:12:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like an accomplice. Dores
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.15,1:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,slammed in my face. Voices
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.84,1:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,accused me terribly of something
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.91,1:12:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.43,1:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,even understand. And Evern, the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.66,1:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,man who swore to protect me,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.68,1:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared for hours and came
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.84,1:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,back
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.13,1:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to look I couldn't decipher. I
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.05,1:12:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to trust him. But every
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.97,1:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,silence of his cut deeper than a
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.03,1:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,knife.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.19,1:12:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Every touch now burned like a
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.52,1:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lie. Now I have to choose. flee
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.00,1:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,before he drags me down with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.25,1:12:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.57,1:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or stay by the side of the man
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.82,1:12:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,who may have orchestrated the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.03,1:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,night that nearly destroyed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.45,1:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if the love that saved
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.88,1:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,me is the same one that planned
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.30,1:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,my ruin?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.51,1:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if every I love you of
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.42,1:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,his was just the price to keep
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.27,1:13:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,me quiet?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.83,1:13:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if in the end the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.40,1:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,escort I rented never stopped
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.14,1:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,being the mafia boss the entire
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.01,1:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,country fears?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.27,1:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, that was just a
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.88,1:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,taste of book two. To watch it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.60,1:13:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,uncensored, just click on the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.26,1:13:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,first
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.55,1:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,link here in the pinned comment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.23,1:13:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you on the other side
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.81,1:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in a few seconds. Remember, just
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.50,1:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,click on the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.13,1:13:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,first link down here in the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.87,1:13:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,comments. And book two,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.35,1:13:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,complete. With no ads or
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.89,1:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,interruptions,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.13,1:13:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll already be available for
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.68,1:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you. It's very simple. Book two
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.29,1:13:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is something I'm loving making,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.89,1:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're loving it too. So I
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.41,1:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,promise there will be more. It's
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.02,1:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,where you find increasingly
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.39,1:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,spicy stories. A true dark
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.97,1:13:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,romance. And precisely because
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.78,1:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,this version is getting more and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.72,1:13:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,more heated,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.89,1:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the video isn't well accepted
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.61,1:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,publicly on YouTube. This closed
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.50,1:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,environment is where I can
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.04,1:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,actually
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.51,1:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,share my essence and where I
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.15,1:13:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,feel free to do my best work for
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.03,1:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you. More news coming soon,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.87,1:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you on the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.20,1:13:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,other side. Unfortunately, many
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.57,1:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,people have been downloading our
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.98,1:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,audio,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.25,1:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,effectively copying the entire
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.94,1:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,story, and simply reposting it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.63,1:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,on YouTube. If you want to
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.09,1:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,watch the original story and be
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.75,1:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the first to receive the next
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.31,1:14:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ones, search for my stories by
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.92,1:14:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lina
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.13,1:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on YouTube to get the best dark
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.94,1:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,romance content. Remember, the
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.68,1:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,official channel is my stories
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.43,1:14:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,by Lina on YouTube. I'll be
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.81,1:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for you there.